  GENERAL-PURPOSE POTENL ROUTINE (MAY 18)

  UNEXPANDED POTENTIAL IS OBTAINED FROM VRTP ROUTINE.

  A SUITABLE VRTP ROUTINE MUST BE SUPPLIED.
 VRTP: loaded Veff0_grid.dat NR=         197  NT=          48
 VRTP: R range [bohr]=   1.5000000000000000        25.000000000000000     
 VRTP: theta range [rad]=   4.9583149999999999E-002   3.0920095000000001     
  IHOMO = 2 SPECIFIES HOMONUCLEAR SYMMETRY.
  USING  48-POINT QUADRATURE FOR THETA-1
